title: Analyst Sentiment and Recommendations for KeyCorp Stock

content.text: Analysts have varying opinions on KeyCorp stock. Some analysts are bullish on the stock, while others are more cautious.

The price targets for KeyCorp stock also vary among analysts. Some analysts have a higher price target, indicating optimism for potential price appreciation, while others have a lower price target, suggesting a more conservative outlook.

When it comes to recommendations, analysts are divided. Some analysts recommend buying KeyCorp stock, citing positive factors such as strong financial performance or potential growth opportunities. On the other hand, some analysts recommend holding or even selling the stock, highlighting concerns such as market risks or potential challenges in the industry.
